data.description: Wonderful investment property with a positive cash flow. Units 1,2, and 3: are 4 bed / 1 bath, hardwood floors, in unit washer and dryer, stove, refrigerator, dishwasher, these 3 units have new tankless water heaters, Central Air A/C. The Garden Unit - 2 bed / 1 bath, title floors, in unit washer and dryer, stove, refrigerator, dishwasher , Water Heater, Central Air A/C. Tenants pay all utilities - Electric and Gas - Heat is Gas.Fully Rehabbed in 2020, New Electric (400 amp serviceUpdated plumping, 2 Car garage, Fenced front and rear with alley access.  Updates throughout, updated kitchens and bathrooms. Laundry in each unit, hardwood flooring, newer appliances (dishwasher included), central air . Kitchens have granite countertops, 42 inch cabinets, large closets for greater storage space, intercom access to the property and apartments. Perfect for the owner occupant looking to have their mortgage paid. Ideally located from downtown Chicago, easy access to I290 in the booming West Garfield Park neighborhood. Schedule a showing today.
